    <item>
      <title>MTG shortcodes demo</title>
      <link>http://localhost:57308/posts/mtg-shortcodes-demo/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 12:00:00 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:57308/posts/mtg-shortcodes-demo/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This post exercises every shortcode the &lt;code&gt;hugo-mtg-shortcodes&lt;/code&gt; module ships.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;inline-mana&#34;&gt;Inline mana&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Hover the symbols below to see the mana font in action: &lt;i class=&#34;ms ms-2 ms-cost ms-shadow&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;ms ms-w ms-cost ms-shadow&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;ms ms-u ms-cost ms-shadow&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; for a tempo deck, &lt;i class=&#34;ms ms-b ms-cost ms-shadow&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;ms ms-b ms-cost ms-shadow&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;ms ms-b ms-cost ms-shadow&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; for ritual decks, &lt;i class=&#34;ms ms-1 ms-cost ms-shadow&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;ms ms-g ms-cost ms-shadow&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; for elf openers.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;a-single-card&#34;&gt;A single card&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;figure class=&#34;card-preview&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://scryfall.com/card/clu/141/lightning-bolt?utm_source=api&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/7/7/77c6fa74-5543-42ac-9ead-0e890b188e99.jpg?1706239968&#34; alt=&#34;Lightning Bolt&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;      &lt;figcaption&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a href=&#34;https://scryfall.com/card/clu/141/lightning-bolt?utm_source=api&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34; class=&#34;card-preview__name&#34;&gt;Lightning Bolt&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;card-preview__type&#34;&gt;Instant&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;inline-card-name-with-hover-preview&#34;&gt;Inline card name with hover preview&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The classic &lt;span class=&#34;cardname&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a class=&#34;cardname__link&#34; href=&#34;https://scryfall.com/card/dsc/113/brainstorm?utm_source=api&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Brainstorm&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;cardname__preview&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img class=&#34;cardname__face&#34; src=&#34;https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/8/b/8beb987c-1b67-4a4e-ae71-58547afad2a0.jpg?1726284649&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt; sees play in cube, legacy, and pauper alike.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
